{"data": [{"id": "4742418", "title": "The Kroger Co. 2024 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by The Kroger Co. in conjunction with their 2024 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106050\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742418-kroger-co-2024-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 21:26:55"}, {"id": "4742399", "title": "Corpay: Fairly Valued At Best", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"paying for gas\" data-id=\"173036652\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">aabejon/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Corpay, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CPAY\" title=\"Corpay, Inc.\">CPAY</a></span>), established in 1986, IPO'd in 2010, and headquartered in Atlanta, Georgia, mainly runs a fuel card business and an accounts payable automation business. It is admittedly very appealing considering the expanding market for its businesses and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173036652/image_173036652.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742399-corpay-fairly-valued-at-best", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 21:24:21"}, {"id": "4742393", "title": "Air France-KLM: Regulations And ULCC Competition Pushing Profits Toward Zero", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Boeing 787 Dreamliner Air France\" data-id=\"1977724210\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Matthieu Douhaire /iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The US airline market faces significant pressure today due to three major factors. One is increased competition from low-cost and ultra-low-cost air carriers, driving profit margins across the industry. Two, most airlines left the pandemic era</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1977724210/image_1977724210.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742393-air-france-klm-regulations-and-ulcc-competition-pushing-profits-toward-zero", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 21:08:49"}, {"id": "4742389", "title": "Pernod Ricard: Very Appealing After A 35% Pullback", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"whisky vodka and gin alcoholic drink beverage bottles at liquor store\" data-id=\"1471719234\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">dimitris_k/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Pernod Ricard (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PDRDF\" title=\"Pernod Ricard SA\">OTCPK:PDRDF</a>, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PRNDY\" title=\"Pernod Ricard SA\">OTCPK:PRNDY</a>) is probably one of the cheapest consumer staples companies capable of generating like-for-like sales growth.</p> <p>The company produces some of the most popular spirits brands such as Absolut, Jameson, and Chivas Regal, and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1471719234/image_1471719234.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742389-pernod-ricard-very-appealing-after-a-35-percent-pullback", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:34:18"}, {"id": "4742400", "title": "Gold ETF Flows: November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"High profits with ETF on the international stock exchanges\" data-id=\"1472468191\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">gopixa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>November in review</span></h2> <p><em>Global physically backed gold ETFs<sup>1</sup> reported a net loss for the first time in six months, with collective outflows of US$2.1bn in November (Table 1).<sup>2</sup></em> Despite a weaker gold price, North America reported a fifth consecutive \u2013 albeit</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472468191/image_1472468191.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742400-gold-etf-flows-november-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:30:00"}, {"id": "4742382", "title": "BNY Mellon Global Emerging Markets Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"banknotes of the BRICS states\" data-id=\"1733709478\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bjoern Wylezich</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <blockquote><p>\u201cWe believe the Fund has exposure to companies with strong return potential and long growth runways.\u201d</p></blockquote> <h2>Market Review</h2> <p>Emerging markets rose strongly in an eventful quarter, which started with political uncertainty in the US and a technology-sector sell-off</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742382-bny-mellon-global-emerging-markets-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:25:00"}, {"id": "4742380", "title": "Century Aluminum: Well-Positioned To Gain From Trump Tariffs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Steel And Aluminum Tariffs\" data-id=\"927991642\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1351px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">wildpixel/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Century Aluminum Company (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CENX\" title=\"Century Aluminum Company\">CENX</a></span>) is a high-momentum stock that stands to benefit significantly if the incoming Trump administration imposes 25% tariffs on imports from Canada, which accounts for about 60% of the total tonnage of aluminum that</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/927991642/image_927991642.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742380-century-aluminum-well-positioned-to-gain-from-trump-tariffs", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:19:10"}, {"id": "4742395", "title": "Brown-Forman Corporation 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Brown-Forman Corporation in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106049\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742395-brown-forman-corporation-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:13:22"}, {"id": "4742378", "title": "Sky Harbour Group: A Unique Business Model", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Large aircraft in aircraft maintenance hangar\" data-id=\"1442422207\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of aviation infrastructure concern <strong>Sky Harbour Group Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SKYH\" title=\"Sky Harbour Group Corporation\">SKYH</a></span>)</strong> have traded between $9 to $12 for most of 2024 as the market awaits three projects coming online in 1Q25. These buildouts near Phoenix, Denver, and Dallas are delayed by three months</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442422207/image_1442422207.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742378-sky-harbour-group-a-unique-business-model", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:07:44"}, {"id": "4742375", "title": "Upstart: Poised For Another Breakout", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Mobile payment. Woman\"s hand has smartphone with banknote in the sky.' data-id=\"1049192158\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3714px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Hiroshi Watanabe</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The stock price of <strong>Upstart Holdings, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UPST\" title=\"Upstart Holdings, Inc.\">UPST</a></span>)</strong> broke out to the upside in November and could potentially, in my view, gather new strength for another challenge of its latest highs.</p> <p>Investor sentiment with respect to Upstart Holdings</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742375-upstart-poised-for-another-breakout", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 20:02:41"}]}